            "en": "16. For I am not ashamed of the gospel, for it is God’s power for salvation to everyone who believes, to the Jew first and also to the Greek.\n17. For the righteousness of God is revealed in the gospel from faith to faith, just as it is written, “The righteous by faith will live.”"
